{"type":null,"faqId":35079,"title":" Can I use my phone as a mobile Wi-Fi hotspot and access the Internet from another device using my phone's data connection?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:end;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>Yes. To activate this, turn on the Wi-Fi hotspot on your phone as follows: </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Choose </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings &gt; Wireless &amp; networks &gt; More &gt; Tethering &amp; portable hotspot &gt; Portable Wi-Fi hotspot</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=111415\" style=\"width:1.96875in;height:3.5006945in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=111416\" style=\"width:1.9680556in;height:3.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=111417\" style=\"width:2.0229166in;height:3.5013888in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>Clicking set up Wi-Fi hotpot，you can set the name(SSID),passwordand security.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=111418\" style=\"width:1.8347223in;height:3.2645833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=111419\" style=\"width:1.8229166in;height:3.2395833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>The test phone open the WLAN hotpot,The auxiliary phone open WLAN to search the test phone’ SSID and connect this WLAN hotpot,it can surf the Internet.</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"9820","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1437034667000,"seriesProductName":"Y541-U02","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"HONOR BEE DUAL SIM ( Y541-U02 )","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}